Our approach





Powering business growth in Europe and beyond 
Europe is a vital market for hundreds of global multinational corporations (MNCs). To thrive in a market that is both commercially mature and at the forefront of technology, you need a technology partner who understands your needs both now and in the future.
Read more 





 Why us? 
 Why us in Europe? 
 3 reasons to choose Orange Business Services 





Wide, deep coverage  
We offer the most comprehensive range of coverage and capabilities to help your organization grow in Europe and thrive globally. Our European operations cover 35 countries and are home to 3,500 staff. To keep you connected, we offer access to the world's largest dedicated MPLS network via more than 1,000 points of presence.
	 





Expertise and experience  
We are a global service provider and systems integrator with more than 700 professional services experts on hand in Europe. This is backed by 300 field engineers, 200 customer service managers and 22 customer program directors, all trained and certified in industry best practices. We are committed to ensuring the highest levels of network and IT integration to give you the best customer experience possible and ensuring business continuity.





Complete package  
Technology convergence is driving business growth and business transformation, and we provide you with everything you need to succeed. Our comprehensive product portfolio enables you to address your new business requirements, while the combination of our deep know-how in networks, recognized position in services and 24/7 support lets you focus on your business while enjoying the utmost peace of mind.










