About Us
We are a manufacturing company based in South Korea, and have distribution centers in San Diego-CA USA and Tijuana-MEXICO. Our Tijuana- Mexico plant is equipped with manufacturing machines and capability to handle various converting services.

Orange Pack Solution specializes in supplying manufacturing industry, with emphasis in Automotive, Electronic, Food and Medical industry with wide range of quality packaging products.  In addition to our general packaging product specialists, we have specialized industry focused departments with Project Managers that are experts in Automotive, Electronic, Food and Medical industries.  Moreover, we offer expertise in customized converting services, producing customized manufacturing solutions with various kinds of specialty materials.

With nearly 30 years of manufacturing experience, we pledge to maintain high standard of quality products, exceptional services, and strive to offer most competitive pricing!












